<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Business Insights - Global Finance Platform</title>
    <style>
        :root { --black-main: #000000; --border-light: #e0e0e0; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; }
        body { background-color: #ffffff; color: var(--black-main); line-height: 1.4; }
        header { padding: 25px 20px; background: #ffffff; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--black-main); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000; }
        .header-wrap { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
        .site-logo { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; display: inline-block; border-bottom: 5px solid var(--black-main); padding-bottom: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        nav { border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light); padding-top: 15px; }
        .nav-menu { display: flex; justify-content: center; list-style: none; gap: 40px; }
        .nav-menu a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--black-main); font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        @media (max-width: 768px) { .nav-menu { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px 25px; } .site-logo { font-size: 30px; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-wrap">
            <a href="/" style="text-decoration:none; color:inherit;">
                <div class="site-logo">FINANCE & BUSINESS INSIGHTS</div>
            </a>
            <nav>
                <ul class="nav-menu">
                    <li><a href="/finance">Finance</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/business">Business</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/ai-tools">AI Tools</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/online-earning">Online Earning</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main style="max-width: 1400px; margin: 80px auto; padding: 20px; text-align: center; min-height: 40vh;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 45px; font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;">Business Section</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #555; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">Welcome to the dedicated Business page. All your insights on international corporate integration, indoor saffron farming, and industrial manufacturing setups will be published here soon.</p>
        <br><br>
        <a href="/" style="padding: 10px 20px; background: black; color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">← Go Back to Home</a>
    </main>

    <footer style="background-color: var(--black-main); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; margin-top: 50px; text-align: center;">
        <div style="max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #777;">&copy; 2026 Kailash Bhisekar. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
